The paper discusses the use of PCA and matrix completion techniques in handling outliers and tracking data in a changing subspace. These topics are commonly studied in the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), information theory (cs.IT), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and signal processing (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
